      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\ude97 I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty ride, and it\u2019s honestly been such a joy to own. It\u2019s in great shape and has clearly been well-loved over the years! It runs super smooth and is totally ready for its next adventure. If you\u2019re looking for a dependable car that looks awesome and drives even better, this is definitely the one for you. Drop me a message if you want to come see it!",
