    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "This vehicle is a remarkable example of a well-maintained daily driver that balances performance with everyday utility. The exterior is finished in a deep Obsidian Metallic that retains a brilliant luster, though a close inspection reveals a few minor stone chips on the forward edge of the hood and a small scuff on the rear passenger-side bumper\u2014typical for a car of this age. It sits on factory 19-inch alloy wheels wrapped in tires with approximately 70% tread life remaining. Inside, the cabin is a sanctuary of premium charcoal leather; the seats are firm and comfortable, with only light creasing on the driver\u2019s side bolster. All electronic features, including the dual-zone climate control, heated seats, and the premium infotainment system, are fully operational. Mechanically, the car is sound. It has been serviced strictly according to the manufacturer's schedule, with a comprehensive folder of receipts included. The engine pulls smoothly, the transmission shifts are crisp, and the brakes provide confident stopping power. This is a solid, reliable vehicle that has been cared for with pride and is ready for its next owner to drive away with confidence.",
